# Package manager
Always use pnpm. Never use npm or yarn.

# Database migrations
Always migrate, never push.
Never run `db:push` or `drizzle-kit push`.
Always use `db:generate` followed by `db:migrate`.
If a migration is needed, run: pnpm db:generate && pnpm db:migrate

# Stack
This project uses SvelteKit, Drizzle ORM, Neon (PostgreSQL), Better Auth, and Anthropic API.

# Svelte
Use Svelte 5 syntax: $state, $derived, $props, $effect. Never use the old Svelte 4 store syntax with $ prefix in components.
Use `onclick` not `on:click`. Use `onsubmit` not `on:submit`.

# TypeScript
Always use TypeScript. Never use plain JavaScript files for logic.
Prefer `type` over `interface` unless extending is needed.

# Environment variables
Server-side secrets use `$env/static/private`.
Public variables use `$env/static/public`.
Never use `process.env` in SvelteKit.

# API routes
All API routes live in `src/routes/api/`.
Always validate input before calling external services.
Always handle errors and return appropriate HTTP status codes.

# AI / Anthropic
Never generate all three outputs at once. Generate `prepare` first, then allow the user to choose `communicate` or `portfolio` separately.
Always use `$env/static/private` for ANTHROPIC_API_KEY.

# File structure
Components live in `src/lib/components/`.
Stores live in `src/lib/stores/`.
AI prompts live in `src/lib/ai/`.
Shared types live in `src/lib/types.ts`.

# Stores
Never use localStorage directly in components. Always use the store wrappers in `src/lib/stores/`.
inputStore persists to localStorage. outputsStore is in-memory only.

# Auth
All routes except `/` and `/auth` require authentication.
Auth is handled by Better Auth. Session is available via `locals.user` in server routes.
Never expose user data in client-side stores.

# Rate limiting
All API routes that call Anthropic must check rate limiting by IP before processing.
Rate limit is 10 requests per IP per hour.

# Styling
Use CSS variables defined in `src/app.css`. Never hardcode colours.
Dark theme only. Background is `--bg: #111111`.
Font families: `--font-sans` for body, `--font-mono` for labels, metadata, and code.
Minimum contrast ratio 4.5:1 for normal text (WCAG AA).

# Components
Always include `aria-label` on icon-only buttons.
Always use semantic HTML — `<button>` for actions, `<a>` for navigation.
Never use `<div>` for interactive elements.

# Decisions flow
The decision input flow lives at `/decisions/new`.
The outputs page lives at `/decisions/outputs`.
Never navigate to `/decisions/outputs` without first setting `outputsStore` with at least `prepare`.
